Class JTreeScopeStackModel

    public class JTreeScopeStackModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    From a scope, get stack of enclosing scopes in order from root down to scope. Then show each scope's (ST's) attributes as children.
